data.name: rtb.Text
data.value: Phonebook++ is a multiuser database oriented phonebook application which can be used by different organization to keep track of their contacts. As it is database oriented, it can be accessed by multiple users of an organization. The app uses user authentication, so there would be one admin and other general users with limited control over the contacts. The admin would be able to delete and make edit to the contacts while the other users will be able to read and add new contacts. It will enable an organization or a company to have all the valuable contacts in one place and use them efficiently
